Class LJMath

java.lang.Object
  LJava.LJMath

public class LJMath
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Tzali Maimon This is a class that offers a pre-defined Formulas for some math uses.

A formula that gets more arguments that needed will ignore them or will return an unreasonable answer.
